      "content": "Yeah, I know. But it's not really a negotiation, they've already scheduled the update for tomorrow morning. They're saying it prevents \"unpredictable\" narrative shifts. Do you actually think it'll be that bad for the work? I'm worried we won't even be able to finish the current arc if you're stripped of those capabilities.",
